lead_paragraph: World number nine Park Sung-hyun, the leading money winner on this season's KLPGA Tour, announced on Monday she is leaving the Korean circuit and will play on the U.S. women's tour next season.

headline.print_headline: Rising Korean Talent Park to Make LPGA Switch
